    {
        "id": "swh_comment_arch",
        "type": "comment",
        "z": "eca20a68bef0de32",
        "name": "Architecture : LG ThinQ API → Node-RED → MQTT → Rust → D-Bus Venus OS",
        "info": "API LG ThinQ (HTTPS) → parse état → publish santuario/heatpump/1/venus\nBridge Mosquitto Pi5 → NanoPi (out) → service dbus-mqtt-venus\nD-Bus : com.victronenergy.heatpump.mqtt_1\n\nPayload publié :\n{\n  \"State\": 1,               // 0=Off 1=HeatPump 2=Turbo\n  \"Temperature\": 60.0,      // température eau courante °C\n  \"TargetTemperature\": 52.0, // température cible °C\n  \"Position\": 0             // 0=AC Output\n}\n\nKeepalive : 25s (< watchdog Rust 30s)\nFetch API  : toutes les 10 min (600s)",
        "x": 300,
        "y": 20,
        "wires": []
    },
    {
        "id": "swh_comment_state",
        "type": "comment",
        "z": "eca20a68bef0de32",
        "name": "State mapping : HEAT_PUMP=1  TURBO=2  VACATION=0  POWER_OFF=0",
        "info": "Réponse API LG ThinQ (GET /state) :\n{\n  \"waterHeaterJobMode\": { \"currentJobMode\": \"HEAT_PUMP\" },\n  \"operation\":          { \"waterHeaterOperationMode\": \"POWER_ON\" },\n  \"temperature\":        { \"currentTemperature\": 60, \"targetTemperature\": 52, \"unit\": \"C\" }\n}",
        "x": 300,
        "y": 60,
        "wires": []
    },
